PrecisAppointment of PATRICIA ANGNAKAK, of Iqaluit, Nunavut, as Deputy Commissioner of Nunavut to execute the office and functions of the Commissioner during his absence or illness or other inability or when the office of Commissioner is vacant, for a term of three years.
